{"vv82:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv82:0.2":"Purisavimana ","vv82:0.3":"Sunikkhittavagga ","vv82:0.4":"8. Anekavannavimanavatthu ","vv82:1.1":"“Anekavannam darasokanasanam, ","vv82:1.2":"Vimanamaruyha anekacittam; ","vv82:1.3":"Parivarito accharasanganena, ","vv82:1.4":"Sunimmito bhutapativa modasi. ","vv82:2.1":"Samassamo natthi kuto panuttaro, ","vv82:2.2":"Yasena punnena ca iddhiya ca; ","vv82:2.3":"Sabbe ca deva tidasagana samecca, ","vv82:2.4":"Tam tam namassanti sasimva deva; ","vv82:2.5":"Ima ca te accharayo samantato, ","vv82:2.6":"Naccanti gayanti pamodayanti. ","vv82:3.1":"Deviddhipattosi mahanubhavo, ","vv82:3.2":"Manussabhuto kimakasi punnam; ","vv82:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhavo, ","vv82:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv82:4.1":"So devaputto attamano, ","vv82:4.2":"…pe… ","vv82:4.3":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv82:5.1":"“Aham bhadante ahuvasi pubbe, ","vv82:5.2":"Sumedhanamassa jinassa savako; ","vv82:5.3":"Puthujjano ananubodhohamasmi, ","vv82:5.4":"So satta vassani paribbajissaham. ","vv82:6.1":"Soham sumedhassa jinassa satthuno, ","vv82:6.2":"Parinibbutassoghatinnassa tadino; ","vv82:6.3":"Ratanuccayam hemajalena channam, ","vv82:6.4":"Vanditva thupasmim manam pasadayim. ","vv82:7.1":"Na masi danam na ca matthi datum, ","vv82:7.2":"Pare ca kho tattha samadapesim; ","vv82:7.3":"Pujetha nam pujaniyassa dhatum, ","vv82:7.4":"Evam kira saggamito gamissatha. ","vv82:8.1":"Tadeva kammam kusalam katam maya, ","vv82:8.2":"Sukhanca dibbam anubhomi attana; ","vv82:8.3":"Modamaham tidasaganassa majjhe, ","vv82:8.4":"Na tassa punnassa khayampi ajjhagan”ti. ","vv82:9.1":"Anekavannavimanam atthamam. "}